{"tid":1142492,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【逃犯條例】民主派批陳維安欺凌論︰以為有人大釋法式行政霸權","createTime":"2019-05-07T06:06:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-07T06:06:11.000Z","uid":241764,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1aab78b5fa0bff42445ac3a31f9fcce5d808401d","tid":1142492,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T06:06:11.000Z","msg":"立法會秘書長陳維安今（7日）早回應《逃犯條例》修例法案委員會爭議，強調秘書處政治中立，不點名批評有人「欺凌」秘書處。民主派會議召集人毛孟靜下午回應稱，陳維安的欺凌說法貽笑大方，強調民主派一直只針對陳維安，而非整個秘書處，批評對方自以為有人大釋法式的行政霸權。<br />\n<br />\n法案委員會的建制派議員早前以「傳閱」形式，以書面表決而非開會討論，決定按內務委員會指引，更換法案委員會主持涂謹申，被民主派質疑缺法理基礎。<br />\n<br />\n議會陣線朱凱廸重申，根據議事規則，除非主席批准，以及無委員反對，否則委員會是不能以傳閱形式作書面表決，他質疑陳維安是否引用「牀下底的守則」，指對方若說不出相關議事規則，便應「收聲」，不應混淆視聽。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190507/s00001/1557207866262/%E3%80%90%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%91%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E6%B4%BE%E6%89%B9%E9%99%B3%E7%B6%AD%E5%AE%89%E6%AC%BA%E5%87%8C%E8%AB%96-%E4%BB%A5%E7%82%BA%E6%9C%89%E4%BA%BA%E5%A4%A7%E9%87%8B%E6%B3%95%E5%BC%8F%E8%A1%8C%E6%94%BF%E9%9C%B8%E6%AC%8A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190507%2Fs00001%2F1557207866262%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B%25E3%2580%2591%25E6%25B0%2591%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E6%2589%25B9%25E9%2599%25B3%25E7%25B6%25AD%25E5%25AE%2589%25E6%25AC%25BA%25E5%2587%258C%25E8%25AB%2596-%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E7%2582%25BA%25E6%259C%2589%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2587%258B%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25BC%258F%25E8%25A1%258C%25E6%2594%25BF%25E9%259C%25B8%25E6%25AC%258A&d=BbGirfR5U81eMP64OYU5HEtrSvVb5AcF94AlmVXjqEc%3D&h=696ea5a8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190507%2Fs00001%2F1557207866262%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B%25E3%2580%2591%25E6%25B0%2591%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E6%2589%25B9%25E9%2599%25B3%25E7%25B6%25AD%25E5%25AE%2589%25E6%25AC%25BA%25E5%2587%258C%25E8%25AB%2596-%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E7%2582%25BA%25E6%259C%2589%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2587%258B%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25BC%258F%25E8%25A1%258C%25E6%2594%25BF%25E9%259C%25B8%25E6%25AC%258A&h=12189855\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190507/s00001/1557207866262/%E3%80%90%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%91%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E6%B4%BE%E6%89%B9%E9%99%B3%E7%B6%AD%E5%AE%89%E6%AC%BA%E5%87%8C%E8%AB%96-%E4%BB%A5%E7%82%BA%E6%9C%89%E4%BA%BA%E5%A4%A7%E9%87%8B%E6%B3%95%E5%BC%8F%E8%A1%8C%E6%94%BF%E9%9C%B8%E6%AC%8A</a>"}]}